response.overview: Revolution Pro presents their 12th Anniversary Show on August 24th, 2024 at the Copper Box Arena in London, England. Matches featured: Connor Mills vs. Ethan Allen Ricky Knight Jr. vs. Zozaya RevPro Undisputed British Cruiserweight Title Six Way Scramble Match Neon (c) vs. El Phantasmo vs. Dante Martin vs. Leon Slater vs. Will Kaven vs. Cameron Khai Tomohiro Ishii vs. JJ Gale No Disqualification Match Debbie Keitel, Gisele Shaw, Kanji, Nightshade & Rhio vs. Cut Throat Collective Donovan Dijak vs. Gabe Kidd RevPro Undisputed British Tag Team Title Match Grizzled Young Veterans (c) vs. Sunshine Machine RevPro Undisputed British Women's Title Match Dani Luna (c) vs. Mina Shirakawa Singles Match Zack Sabre Jr. vs. Hechicero RevPro Undisputed British Heavyweight Title Match Michael Oku (c) vs. Luke Jacobs
response.title: RevPro 12th Anniversary Show
